元起" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">机械师曙光 16Air 酷睿版</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 4599 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/Nz3xFa3" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/227782/25/12927/99191/65a77bc8F456c2be0/929c45d6ac83f849.jpg" title="机械师上架多款曙光系列笔记本：i7-13620H 处理器，4599 元起" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">机械师曙光 15Mate</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">5999 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/NqywVvt" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/69950/22/18020/97633/65aa4541F29c23ac6/ada4abd9c81f001f.jpg" title="机械师上架多款曙光系列笔记本：i7-13620H 处理器，4599 元起" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">机械师曙光 16</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">7999 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
